Wala naman tayong gaanong maraming patakaran dito.

538
00:25:38,880 --> 00:25:39,480
Umupo.

539
00:25:44,350 --> 00:25:45,110
Binibini,

540
00:25:46,440 --> 00:25:47,350
Gusto ko

541
