588
00:27:54,960 --> 00:27:55,640
Bukod pa rito,

589
00:27:56,750 --> 00:27:57,480
Li Zhen,

590
00:27:58,640 --> 00:27:59,720
ang iyong pamilya

591
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:01,550
