631
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,440
Paalam.

632
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:54,520
Ah, tama.

633
00:29:54,920 --> 00:29:56,030
Nakalimutan kong banggitin ito—

634
00:29:56,030 --> 00:29:57,030
