00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:52,200
Lumuhod!

666
00:31:56,270 --> 00:31:57,440
Yumuko!

667
00:31:59,240 --> 00:32:00,350
Bumangon ka!

668
00:32:00,350 --> 00:32:02,480
Hindi ba't napatalsik si Eighth Master Li?

669
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:04,410
Seremonya ito ng sentenaryo.

670
00:32:04,650 --> 00:32:06,410
Maaaring tumanggi ang mga ninuno na kilalanin ang
Ikawalong Guro na si Li,

671
00:32:06,410 --> 00:32:08,740
