727
00:34:13,800 --> 00:34:15,630
Ano ang hindi mo pa nagawa?

728
00:34:17,030 --> 00:34:17,760
Kung ako ikaw,

729
00:34:17,760 --> 00:34:19,070
Pupunta sana ako sa mundong ilalim

730
00:34:19,070 --> 00:34:22,000
